    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who prioritizes both performance and mechanical integrity. It remains in commendable condition, exhibiting a well-preserved aesthetic and a robust powertrain that reflects a history of diligent maintenance. This offering provides a sophisticated driving experience and represents a secure investment in reliable, high-caliber transportation. Professional inspection confirms its readiness for immediate service.",
